{{!
    @template mod_booking/slotbooking/slot_grid_day

    Stacked day list for the fixed-grid (calendar) booking interface: bookable slots and
    warmup/cooldown buffer separators are rendered as ordinary block rows, one after another
    (not positioned proportionally to real elapsed time). Bookable rows keep a minimum
    readable height and never shrink further; buffer separators are a small constant height
    regardless of the configured minutes. The container scrolls if the day's rows don't fit.
    The condition/slotBooking picker builds the block list and wires the click handlers; this
    template only renders the markup.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * blocks - Slot rows and buffer separators, in chronological order.
        * key - Slot key "start:end" (buffer separators use a synthetic "buffer:..." key).
        * statusclass - Modifier class (booking-slot--available|--selected|--booked|--buffer).
        * buffer - True for a buffer separator: renders as a plain fixed-height block with no
          header/content and is skipped by the click handler (see slot_day_renderers.js).
        * time - Time range label, e.g. "16:00 - 16:20". Only used when not buffer.
        * booked - Whether the slot is already booked.
        * bookedlabel - Label shown on booked slots.
        * priceformatted - Formatted price, empty when no price applies.
        * teachers - Teacher summary string, empty when none.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "blocks": [
            {"key": "1620:1640", "statusclass": "booking-slot--available", "time": "16:00 - 16:20", "booked": false, "bookedlabel": "Booked", "priceformatted": "", "teachers": ""},
            {"key": "buffer:1620:1640:trailing", "statusclass": "booking-slot--buffer", "buffer": true}
        ]
    }
}}
<div class="booking-slot-timeline booking-slot-timeline--fixed border rounded d-flex flex-column">
    {{#blocks}}
        <div class="booking-slot {{statusclass}}" data-slot-key="{{key}}" {{#booked}}data-booked="1"{{/booked}}>
            {{^buffer}}
                <div class="booking-slot-header">
                    <div class="booking-slot-time">{{time}}</div>
                    {{#booked}}<div class="booking-slot-badge">{{bookedlabel}}</div>{{/booked}}
                    {{#priceformatted}}<div class="booking-slot-price">{{priceformatted}}</div>{{/priceformatted}}
                </div>
                {{#teachers}}<div class="booking-slot-teachers">{{teachers}}</div>{{/teachers}}
            {{/buffer}}
        </div>
    {{/blocks}}
</div>
